I’m a skateboarder but most importantly i love Jesus. This is my 10th year of being a follower of the WAY. Went to Mexico shared the gospel with people at a fat downtown party. At one point as I was dancing someone thought I was taking drugs but I said nooo it’s Jesus 😂 .  Saw people give their life to Jesus and encounter Him. People got supernaturally healed. I’m on a different high. God set me free from depression and suicidal thoughts I’m so glad He did!!! Devil tried to fool me but Jesus had a better plan and made me a friend. Wow wow wow. Jesus is the answer. THANKS ALL WHO GAVE TO THIS TRIP. 🫶🏽🫶🏽🫶🏽 DM me if you got questions about Jesus or def would like to pray for ya.

I’m always slaying fear in my life. 
The sword which is the word of God is the weapon. It’s sharp. Just like the story of David and Goliath. 
God was the source of His strength. 
Intimacy with God + skill = gave David victory. Fear taunts. Fear keeps you from moving forward. Fear keeps you in the “safe place”. Fear keeps you from dreaming bigger with God. Live in faith and stop watching fear eat your life. Fear is a cockroach 🪳don’t let it multiply. Bless upppp. 😁

6 TIPS ON **HOW TO BE A GOOD SKATEBOARDER.**

1. Your Character matters: my opinion the first thing you should focus on is being nice. Don’t be a jerk be cool. Don’t snake people be considerate of others around you. 
2. Watch skate videos and pull inspiration from them.
3. Skate street and transition. 
4. Learn new tricks 
5. Put in time: the more you skate the better you get. 
6. Skate with others
